-## Rollback Procedure
-
-If issues arise, rollback using:
-```bash
-# Reinstall taskX
-pip install taskx==0.1.0
-
-# Revert configuration files from git
-git checkout .taskx-pin .gitmodules
-
-# Restore original scripts
-git checkout scripts/taskx
-```
-
